title: analytics-log
text:
Duplicate per week: cp -R w_template/ w1/ then rename files.
Update Quarto _quarto.yml to include projects/ or w*/report.qmd in the build.

Week 3 (ML): add models/ for saved .pkl/.joblib files. Week 5 (BI): drop ERD PDFs in output/diagrams/. Week 6 (end-to-end): you might nest a mini-app or API; put that under src/ or service/.
